wicket.contrib.tinymce4.settings

Class Button

  • java.lang.Object
    • wicket.contrib.tinymce4.settings.Enum
      • wicket.contrib.tinymce4.settings.Button
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Button
extends Enum
    Base class for tinymce button. There ae two types of buttons:
    • default button - these buttons are defined in TinyMCESettings class.
    • plugin button - these buttons are defined by individual plugins.
    Author:
    Iulian-Corneliu COSTAN
